name: Experiment Or Die #107
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. When I was a kid I was obsessed with explorers. When we learned about these men that traveled the unknown seeking out new lands, I wished it was me. I learned everything about the men that mapped the planet earth, and as an adult I'm still incredibly interested in exploring new worlds. However I feel that the Metaverse is much more in reach than say the bottom of the ocean, or Mars. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
